attacks.text: This attack does 20 more damage for each of your Benched Pokémon.

ability.name: Fabled Luster
ability.text: This Pokémon can’t be affected by any Special Conditions.

ability.name: Toughness Aroma
ability.text: Each of your {G} Pokémon gets +20 HP.

ability.name: Dismantling Keys
ability.text: Once during your turn, if this Pokémon is on your Bench, you may discard all Pokémon Tools from your opponent’s Active Pokémon. If you do, discard this Pokémon.

name: Flame Patch
text: Attach a {R} Energy from your discard pile to your Active {R} Pokémon.

attacks.name: Spark
attacks.text: This attack also does 10 damage to 1 of your opponent’s Benched Pokémon.

attacks.name: Surprise Attack
attacks.text: Flip a coin. If tails, this attack does nothing.

attacks.name: Bubble
attacks.text: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent’s Active Pokémon is now Paralyzed.

attacks.name: Flash Impact
attacks.text: This attack also does 20 damage to 1 of your Benched Pokémon.

attacks.name: Giant Twister
attacks.text: Flip 3 coins. For each heads, discard a random Energy from your opponent’s Active Pokémon. If all of them are tails, this attack does nothing.

attacks.name: Darkness Claw
attacks.text: Your opponent reveals their hand. Choose a Supporter card you find there and discard it.

attacks.name: Balloon Barrage
attacks.text: This attack does 20 more damage for each Energy attached to this Pokémon.

ability.name: Boosted Evolution
ability.text: As long as this Pokémon is in the Active Spot, it can evolve during your first turn or the turn you play it.

attacks.name: Copy a Friend
attacks.text: Choose 1 of your Benched Pokémon’s attacks, except any Pokémon ex, and use it as this attack. If this Pokémon doesn’t have the necessary Energy to use that attack, this attack does nothing.

attacks.name: Fire Fang
attacks.text: Flip a coin. If heads, your opponent’s Active Pokémon is now Burned.

attacks.name: Expert Splasher
attacks.text: Flip 2 coins. If both of them are heads, this attack does 20 more damage.

attacks.name: Chomp Chomp Bite
attacks.text: Flip a coin until you get tails. For each heads, discard a random Energy from your opponent’s Active Pokémon.

attacks.name: Find a Friend
attacks.text: Put a random Pokémon from your deck into your hand.
